headline: Target wants to revive ‘Tar-zhay.’ It just debuted a preview of that in New York
summary: Target hopes that a recapturing of its cultural cachet will spark a turnaround for its business. It’s turning to a fashion-forward New York neighborhood to get started.

headline: Walmart's Valuation Makes Zero Mathematical Sense
summary: Walmart trades at an extreme valuation with a 40x P/E, lagging yields, ~10% growth outlook, and echoes of its 2000-era peak. Read why WMT stock is a strong sell.
